text: Thomas Ackland Blundell (born 1 September 1990 in Wellington, New Zealand) is a New Zealand cricketer who plays for Wellington in the Plunket Shield. He made his international debut in January 2017 and has scored four test centuries in test cricket. ==Other websites== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Wellington
